      "updated": 1757395536520,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When to use?\n1. Async processing like in case of youtube example:\n    client -> upload server --> queues -> transcoding server to transcode. \n\n2. Decouple producer and consumer.\n   Leetcode example: two parts one is for running the code and another is handle the consumers in the contest.\n     Clients --> LC service ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When to use?\n1. Async processing like in case of youtube example:\n    client -> upload server --> queues -> transcoding server to transcode. \n\n2. Decouple producer and consumer.\n   Leetcode example: two parts one is for running the code and another is handle the consumers in the contest.\n     Clients --> LC service ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
