      "updated": 1757396122742,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Azure Event hub and service bus overview:\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Azure Event hub and service bus overview:\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "G9zw0-x5aFQ3CLtNsOnZk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3072.3677438650493,
      "y": -10924.453437459693,
      "width": 1470.918701171875,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 90,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "am",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 425874612,
      "version": 598,
      "versionNonce": 1273288884,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1757396292708,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Event hub is for events streaming. Support atleast one delivery by default. Handles pub-sub also. Supports consumer groups. THis is the native data\nstreaming service in azure\nService bus: fully managed enterprise message broker with messsage queues and pub-sub topics. It has subscriptions, pub-sub, queues and topics. It is\nused in applications to scale independently. It also has exactly once semantics, there some transaction rules are being used. \n\nLittle bit idea on chatgpt on same topic: https://chatgpt.com/share/68bfbd2e-e024-800f-b934-b4b94df26b96",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Event hub is for events streaming. Support atleast one delivery by default. Handles pub-sub also. Supports consumer groups. THis is the native data\nstreaming service in azure\nService bus: fully managed enterprise message broker with messsage queues and pub-sub topics. It has subscriptions, pub-sub, queues and topics. It is\nused in applications to scale independently. It also has exactly once semantics, there some transaction rules are being used. \n\nLittle bit idea on chatgpt on same topic: https://chatgpt.com/share/68bfbd2e-e024-800f-b934-b4b94df26b96",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3MxlTB1FpS0vXSY6QToDM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3058.625101161314,
      "y": -10640.485702711874,
      "width": 292.519775390625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
