      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773030073509,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "offset information is also there, for each \nmessage being read by consumer group.\n\nmaintained in kafka for each CG. \nPost reading message, it is being commited \nin kafka upto what it has been read.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "offset information is also there, for each \nmessage being read by consumer group.\n\nmaintained in kafka for each CG. \nPost reading message, it is being commited \nin kafka upto what it has been read.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
